item.title: Interesting Web Analysis software
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: Wired article about some website analysis software that renders your site traffic in a "SimCity"-like environment. "Buildings grow and shrink in real time proportionate to the number of visitors on your site" (Link courtesy of Slashdot)
